PART 8: CONE ITERATIONS — BUILDING THE TOWER
======================================================================

  CONE TOWER starting from C_3 (cyclic):
  n=3: H = 3 (C_3)
  n=4: H = 3 (dom_cone^1(C_3))
  n=5: H = 3 (dom_cone^2(C_3))
  n=6: H = 3 (dom_cone^3(C_3))
  n=7: H = 3 (dom_cone^4(C_3))

  CONE TOWER starting from T_3 (transitive):
  n=3: H = 1 (T_3)
  n=4: H = 1 (dom_cone^1(T_3))
  n=5: H = 1 (dom_cone^2(T_3))
  n=6: H = 1 (dom_cone^3(T_3))
  n=7: H = 1 (dom_cone^4(T_3))

  MIXED CONE TOWER from C_3:
  n=3: H = 3 (C_3)
  n=4: H = 3 (dom_cone(C_3))
  n=5: H = 3 (domd_cone(dom_cone(C_3)))
  n=6: H = 3 (dom_cone(domd_cone(dom_cone(C_3))))
  n=7: H = 3 (domd_cone(dom_cone(domd_cone(dom_cone(C_3)))))

